512
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:23,880
That esophageal injury. I just--

513
00:28:24,290 --> 00:28:26,200
I didn't know how I could've missed it.

514
00:28:27,930 --> 00:28:31,110
Well, they're easy to miss.
I missed it, too, remember?

515
00:28:31,910 --> 00:28:34,600
So you're fine. No reaming today.

516
00:28:36,260 --> 00:28:38,190
You want to take him or are you too tired?

517
00:28:38,570 --> 00:28:40,270
You've both been going since you got here.

518
00:28:40,670 --> 00:28:43,799
