to take him if that's okay.

519
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:45,980
Good. O.R. 1 is prepped and ready.

520
00:28:45,990 --> 00:28:47,050
You can take him there.

521
00:28:47,470 --> 00:28:49,150
Bobby, you want to scrub in with her?

522
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:49,920
Happy to, sir.

523
00:28:49,921 --> 00:28:50,860
Good.

524
00:28:55,500 --> 00:28:57,140
Not too tired for surgery?

525
00:28:57,760 --> 00:29:00,200
I am never too tired for surgery.

526
00:29:04,460 --> 00:29:05,140
Okay.

