00:29:55,900 --> 00:29:58,320
Anyone got another camera?
My battery is dead.

534
00:30:07,270 --> 00:30:11,489
Oh, holy crap.
I nicked the friggin' artery.

535
00:30:11,490 --> 00:30:12,650
Clamp it.

536
00:30:15,120 --> 00:30:16,710
Little slow on the uptake there.

537
00:30:17,340 --> 00:30:18,570
You're welcome?

538
00:30:19,770 --> 00:30:21,650
I'm sorry, Bobby. 
Thank you.

