00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:13,840
Hey, what is that, son?

559
00:31:14,620 --> 00:31:17,370
Oh. Uh, it's-- it's nothing, sir.

560
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:19,180
Um, the frag vest absorbed the impact.

561
00:31:19,181 --> 00:31:22,100
Didn't even break the skin.
Still, get it looked at.

562
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:23,960
Sure, sir, but really, it's nothing.

563
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:27,970
Yes, sir.

